title: Catasauqua's Quinn Bachman is lehighvalleylive Field Hockey Player of the Week
text:
By Tom Hinkel | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 08, 2015 7:00 AM 
FIELD HOCKEY PLAYER OF THE WEEK Quinn Bachman (lehighvalleylive.com file photo) 
Quinn Bachman , Catasauqua 
Bachman, a senior forward, produced seven goals and three assists in the Rough Riders' 2-0 week. 
She tallied three goals and an assist in a 4-0 decision over Saucon Valley, and followed with four goals and two assists in a 10-1 romp over Wilson. 
Bachman, who also plays basketball and runs track at Catty, had 18 goals and 10 assists through 12 games this season. 
Honorable mention : Jr. M Anissa Abboud , Liberty; Jr. G Ashley Kunsman , Northampton; So. G Kate Gogel , Northampton; Jr. M Cheyenne Ott , Bangor; So. F Meghan Reese , Southern Lehigh; Jr. F Mayv Clune , Moravian Academy; Julia Dalrymple , Phillipsburg; Rebecca Sigman , Warren Hills.
